            <div class="entry">
                <p>Hey Ole Man!!!</p>
                <p>It's been a rough past few weeks without you... It's not the same without you.</p>
                <p>Today's Fathers Day! Happy Fathers Day Ole Man!!! I really missed you today.. we were unstoppable together. Not much new since the last time we talked.. I flew down to Ma on Mothers Day... I got the last flight to make sure she wasn't alone, you were always there, and you always made sure I was! When I found out you couldn't be with us anymore, I did exactly what you would've told me to do in that situation! I made it on time! Me and Ma spent a little over an hour together this Mothers Day... I wish it were that easy for this Fathers Day...</p>
                <p>I hope you're safe and happy. I hope you're okay and everything is what you wanted it to be. I hope I get to see you again.</p>
                <br>
                <br>
                <p>Love always,</p>
                <br>
                <p>Jr.</p>
